Title: Collection of California Fruit Labels, ca. 1905-1949
Description.abstract: Collection consists of fruit labels used by California growers. Most are for oranges and lemons, but also include grapefruit, apples, pears, melons, and grapes. Growers include Rialto Orange Company and Fillmore Citrus Association.
